<p style="Caption" xid="2204"><c props="font-style:italic">Linux Filesystem Hierarchy Standard - items not bold from above will not be included</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2205">There are 3 additional libraries that are non-standard but appear on pretty much all Linux distros <field footnote-id="50" text:note-citation="51" type="footnote_ref" xid="2206" props="text-position:superscript"></field><foot footnote-id="50" xid="2207">
<p style="Footnote" xid="2208"><field type="footnote_anchor" footnote-id="50" xid="2209"></field>	<a xlink:href="http://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/FHS_3.0/fhs/ch03s02.html" xid="2210">http://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/FHS_3.0/fhs/ch03s02.html</a></p>
