</cell>
<cell xid="2223" props="left-attach:1; right-attach:2; bot-style:none; bot-attach:3; top-attach:2; right-style:none; top-style:none; left-style:none">
<p style="Table Contents" xid="2224" props="text-align:center">Home directory for the root user - not to be confused with /</p>
</cell>
<cell xid="2225" props="left-attach:0; right-attach:1; bot-style:none; bot-attach:4; top-attach:3; right-style:none; top-style:none; left-style:none">
<p style="Table Contents" xid="2226"><c props="font-weight:bold">lib64</c></p>
</cell>
<cell xid="2227" props="left-attach:1; right-attach:2; bot-style:none; bot-attach:4; top-attach:3; right-style:none; top-style:none; left-style:none">
<p style="Table Contents" xid="2228" props="text-align:center">Alternate home for 64 bit libraries</p>
</cell>
</table>
<p style="FigureWithCaption" xid="2229"><c></c></p>
<p style="Caption" xid="2230"><c props="font-style:italic">Ubuntu 15.04 root full directory listing</c></p>
