<p style="Heading 4" xid="2233">/usr standard subdirectories</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2234">There are a series of standard directory locations that are under /usr that you need to know as well.</p>
<p style="Text body" xid="2235">/usr</p>
<table xid="2236" props="table-row-heights:///////">
<cell xid="2237" props="left-attach:0; right-attach:1; bot-style:none; bot-attach:1; top-attach:0; right-style:none; top-style:none; left-style:none">
<p style="Table Heading" xid="2238">sub-directory</p>
</cell>
<cell xid="2239" props="left-attach:1; right-attach:2; bot-style:none; bot-attach:1; top-attach:0; right-style:none; top-style:none; left-style:none">
