<p style="Heading 1" xid="3523">Creating, Partitioning, and Mounting Filesystems</p>
<p style="FigureWithCaption" xid="3524"><c></c></p>
<p style="Caption" xid="3525"><c props="font-style:italic">Easy as cake...</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3526"><c props="font-weight:bold">Chapter 12 Objectives</c></p>
<p style="Text body" xid="3527"><c props="font-weight:bold">Outcomes</c></p>
<p style="Heading 2" xid="3528">Types</p>
<p level="3" listid="1398" parentid="1389" xid="3529" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; default-tab-interval:0.4925in; margin-left:2.540000cm; lang:en-US; text-indent:-0.635000cm; list-style:Bullet List; margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in; font-size:12pt; field-font:NULL"><field type="list_label" xid="3530"></field>	Creating them virtually</p>
<p level="3" listid="1398" parentid="1389" xid="3531" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; default-tab-interval:0.4925in; margin-left:2.540000cm; lang:en-US; text-indent:-0.635000cm; list-style:Bullet List; margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in; font-size:12pt; field-font:NULL"><field type="list_label" xid="3532"></field>	fdisk<br/></p>
<p level="3" listid="1398" parentid="1389" xid="3533" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; default-tab-interval:0.4925in; margin-left:2.540000cm; lang:en-US; text-indent:-0.635000cm; list-style:Bullet List; margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in; font-size:12pt; field-font:NULL"><field type="list_label" xid="3534"></field>	df</p>
<p level="3" listid="1398" parentid="1389" xid="3535" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; default-tab-interval:0.4925in; margin-left:2.540000cm; lang:en-US; text-indent:-0.635000cm; list-style:Bullet List; margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in; font-size:12pt; field-font:NULL"><field type="list_label" xid="3536"></field>	mount command</p>
<p level="3" listid="1398" parentid="1389" xid="3537" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; default-tab-interval:0.4925in; margin-left:2.540000cm; lang:en-US; text-indent:-0.635000cm; list-style:Bullet List; margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in; font-size:12pt; field-font:NULL"><field type="list_label" xid="3538"></field>	/etc/fstab</p>
